                            <p class="text-gray-700">Where appropriate, engaging with the infringing party (e.g., government department) and issuing formal notices of intention to litigate, as required by law (e.g., Institution of Legal Proceedings Against Organs of State Act).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start group">
